<Layout title="DRMS — SAP Middleware - Mas Muhammad" description="An enterprise SAP Business ByDesign integration middleware comprising two components: a REST API gateway that exposes SAP ERP functions (sales orders, credit notes, returns, stock transfers) as JSON endpoints for external applications, and a background scheduler that periodically extracts SAP master/transactional data to CSV files for a third-party B2B analytics gateway.">
